{"word":"ἐκπορεύομαι","slug":"ἐκπορεύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐϰπορεύομαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκ\">ἐκ</a>, πορεύομαι</el>] the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> common since Xenophon, ‘move from one place to another’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b>go (out), come (out) <a href='B:470 3:5'>Mt 3:5</a>; <a href='B:480 1:5'>Mk 1:5</a>; <a href='B:500 5:29'>J 5:29</a>; <a href='B:510 25:4'>Ac 25:4</a> (leave). <p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of things: refuse <b><a href='B:480 7:19'>Mk 7:19</a>;</b> lightning <b><a href='B:730 4:5'>Rv 4:5</a>;</b> fire<b> <a href='B:730 9:17'>9:17</a>;</b> stream of water <b><a href='B:730 22:1'>22:1</a> (flow out);</b> a word <b><a href='B:470 4:4'>Mt 4:4</a>; <a href='B:470 15:11'>15:11</a>; <a href='B:480 7:15'>Mk 7:15</a>; <a href='B:490 4:22'>Lk 4:22</a>; <a href='B:560 4:29'>Eph 4:29</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκπνέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐκπορνεύω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}